Please don't misunderstand.  This is NOT the iTunes set.  The iTunes set is in lossy AAC format.  

These files were taken from the recent remasters in Apple Lossless.  This allows uncompressed audio quality PLUS you can import them directly into iTunes without the need of converting FLAC files.
